# Hooke Hub

This is a documentation-only hub repository. It contains no source code.

## Do

- Keep the README repository tables accurate and consistently formatted.
- Use canonical GitHub URLs when linking to repositories.
- Write in clear, concise Markdown.
- Follow the conventions in AGENTS.md and CONTRIBUTING.md.

## Do not

- Add application or library source code to this repo.
- Add package manifests, build configs, or CI pipelines that build software.
- Reference files or internals of other repositories — link to them instead.
